vaa magale vaa is a 1994 tamil drama film directed visu .   the film features visu , kushboo , rekha and veera pandiyan in the lead roles , with delhi ganesh , charle , thyagu , t. p. gajendran and t. s. balachander playing supporting roles .   the film , produced by n. ramasamy , had musical score by deva and was released on 4 december 1994 .